  "description": "Solomon at strandTune=4.0 creates two rings a major third apart — the two-ring architecture becomes a built-in harmonic dyad coupled through the Solomon cross-link matrix. At macroKnot=0.5, one ring receives gentle directional asymmetry from the Trefoil blend: the major third relationship is lopsided in a subtle, mathematical way that makes it feel alive. The LFO at 0.02 Hz breathes the topology on a 50-second cycle — so slow that the modulation is never consciously perceived, only felt. Maximum reverb: the kelp forest at its deepest. Play one note and wait.",
